{"tid":1287450,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"二手樓價指數破頂  按周升1.41%","createTime":"2019-07-05T08:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T23:20:06.000Z","uid":39027,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5df49a00f5d25a66b4fbaa6cacb81fe7f9f1dbaa","tid":1287450,"uid":39027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:15:06.000Z","msg":"二手樓價再升，中原城市領先指數CCL最新報190.48點，按周升1.41%，連升3周再創歷史新高。中原城市大型屋苑領先指數CCL Mass報191.58點，按周升1.53%。CCL(中小型單位)報190.19點，按周升1.47%。CCL(大型單位)報191.93點，按周升1.10%。CCL、CCL Mass及CCL(中小型單位)齊升3周，分別上升2.27%、2.28%及2.30%。<br />\n<br />\n本周四區指數二升二跌。新界西CCL_Mass報174.59點，按周升1.86%，連升4周共2.30%。在剛需支持下，新界西樓價持續高企。港島CCL_Mass報199.24點，按周升5.69%，連升2周共6.62%。九龍CCL_Mass報185.72點，按周跌0.95%，連升2周後回軟。新界東CCL_Mass報199.35點，按周跌0.30%，連跌2周共0.82%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190705/bkn-20190705160136854-0705_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190705%2Fbkn-20190705160136854-0705_00842_001.html&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=1a778ae8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190705/bkn-20190705160136854-0705_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2247b3713f6a3a21f2db6f5fd980420db2f364f4","tid":1287450,"uid":87471,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"其實究竟升乜撚柒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74774b0866c049064987c17805c82a1b4a38c80","tid":1287450,"uid":59492,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:34:16.000Z","msg":"只有修例才能令樓價回復正常水平"},{"pid":"2b6cf9c91aaf36cbce339e5667c7f1fcc9312846","tid":1287450,"uid":30109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:57:51.000Z","msg":"真係唔明升嘅原因，但產業署嗰個指數仲升得勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df85f58fb44b80aee9137c0348dbd5b54f5c0c02","tid":1287450,"uid":100173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid"